OL,6,FTwo-year-old , 60, at their basement
OL,7,Fflat in Prince Alfred Avenue,
OL,8,FSkegness, on 9 January.JThe inquest,
OL,9,Fopened by senior coroner Paul Smith in
OL,10,FLincoln, heard how Bronson went to
OL,11,Flive with his father after his parents
OL,12,Fseparated in the summer of 2022. His
OL,13,Ftwo siblings lived with his mother.
OL,14,FDet Insp Claire Rimmer, of
OL,15,FLincolnshire Police, told the
OL,16,Fcoroner's court how police were called
OL,17,Fby a "concerned" neighbour who had not
OL,18,Fseen Mr Battersby for some time and
OL,19,Freported a smell coming from the flat.
