OL,6,FHis body was found behind the living
OL,7,Froom door after a suspected heart
OL,8,Fattack. Bronson was found dead between
OL,9,Fhis father's legs.
OL,11,FThe court heard from coroner's officer
OL,12,FTracy Cox, who confirmed that
OL,13,FBronson's post-mortem examination took
OL,14,Fplace at Leicestershire Royal
OL,15,FInfirmary on 11 January. The report
OL,16,Fconfirmed Bronson died because of
OL,17,Fdehydration.JMr Smith adjourned the
OL,18,Finquest, saying a "thorough and
OL,19,Fsensitive investigation" was taking
OL,20,Fplace into the two deaths.
