OL,6,FBronson and his father were found dead
OL,7,Fby the property's landlady and a
OL,8,Fsocial worker.
OL,10,FIt came a week after social workers
OL,11,Fvisited the home on 2 January, but
OL,12,Freceived no answer when they tried to
OL,13,Fmake contact.
OL,15,FFurther attempts to reach them two
OL,16,Fdays later again failed and police
OL,17,Fwere called, but it took another five
OL,18,Fdays before the bodies were discovered.
