OL,6,FThe Lincolnshire Safeguarding Children
OL,7,FPartnership is carrying out of the
OL,8,Fcase, which began in February and is
OL,9,Fexpected to take six months.
OL,11,Fsaid the deaths are not being treated
OL,12,Fas suspicious, but the force has
OL,13,Freferred itself to the Independent
OL,14,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC) over
OL,15,Fthe incident.
OL,17,FThe watchdog has confirmed it will
OL,18,Finvestigate.
